Package: adhesiomeR
Type: Package
Title: Analysis of the adhesiome in R
Version: 1.0
LazyData: TRUE
Date: 2020-05-19
Authors@R: c(person("Katarzyna", "Sidorczuk", 
           email = "sidorczuk.katarzyna17@gmail.com",
           role = c("cre", "aut"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6576-9054")))
Description: AdhesiomeR contains the most comprehensive, manually curated set of E. coli adhesins and offers a powerful analysis framework, called adhesiomeR, that enables qualitative inspection of the adhesin repertoires. Together, these resources offer a convenient analysis of adhesin genes in E. coli genomes. 
